OL,3,CDonald Trump says countries are
OL,4,C'happy' with tariffs as he vows to
OL,5,Ckeep them
OL,7,FUS President Donald Trump has said he
OL,8,Fwill continue imposing tariffs on
OL,9,Fother countries despite the Supreme
OL,10,FCourt ruling that overturned the
OL,11,Fimport tax policy.
OL,13,FMr Trump's latest trade tariffs came
OL,14,Finto effect on UK imports at 10% on
OL,15,FTuesday, lower than the 15% rate he
OL,16,Fthreatened over the weekend, after he
OL,17,Fsigned an executive order following
OL,18,Fthe Supreme Court's decision on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
