OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772012418
OL,3,CDonald Trump says countries are
OL,4,C'happy' with tariffs as he vows to
OL,5,Ckeep them
OL,7,F"Countries that were ripping us off
OL,8,Ffor decades are now paying us hundreds
OL,9,Fof millions of dollars. Yet these
OL,10,Fcountries are now happy and so are we.
OL,11,FWe made deals. The deals are all done.
OL,12,FAnd they're happy."
OL,14,FMr Trump said "many of the wars I
OL,15,Fsettled" were because of the "threat
OL,16,Fof tariffs".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@SO]vD@OOUwD@HO]wD@^OUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
