OL,3,CDonald Trump says countries are
OL,4,C'happy' with tariffs as he vows to
OL,5,Ckeep them
OL,7,F"Tariffs, paid for by foreign
OL,8,Fcountries will, like in the past,
OL,9,Fsubstantially replace the modern-day
OL,10,Fsystem of income tax, taking a great
OL,11,Ffinancial burden off the people that I
OL,12,Flove," he said.
OL,14,F"Trillions and trillions of dollars
OL,15,Fwill be pouring into the United States
OL,16,Fof America, because we finally have a
OL,17,Fpresident who puts America first."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@FO]vD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
