OL,3,CDonald Trump says countries are
OL,4,C'happy' with tariffs as he vows to
OL,5,Ckeep them
OL,7,FElsewhere in the speech, Mr Trump
OL,8,Fannounced a "war on fraud" headed by
OL,9,FVice President JD Vance, saying
OL,10,Fmembers of the Somali community in
OL,11,FMinnesota had "pillaged an estimated
OL,12,F19 billion dollars (#14 billion) from
OL,13,Fthe American taxpayer".
OL,15,FHe said: "We have all of the
OL,16,Finformation. And in actuality, the
OL,17,Fnumber is much higher than California,
OL,18,FMassachusetts, Maine, many other
OL,19,Fstates are even worse."
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@ZO]sD@OOUuD@VO]wD@JOU{D@WO]
