OL,3,CDonald Trump says countries are
OL,4,C'happy' with tariffs as he vows to
OL,5,Ckeep them
OL,7,FLabelling Iran as the "world's number
OL,8,Fone sponsor of terror", the president
OL,9,Fsaid he could never allow the country
OL,10,Fto have a nuclear weapon
OL,12,F"We are in negotiations with them," he
OL,13,Fsaid. "They want to make a deal, but
OL,14,Fwe haven't heard those secret words,
OL,15,F'we will never have a nuclear weapon'.
OL,17,F"My preference is to solve this
OL,18,Fproblem through diplomacy."
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@VO]tD@AOUtD@cO]uD@GOUyD@AOUzD@
OL,26,A[O]
