OL,3,CDonald Trump says countries are
OL,4,C'happy' with tariffs as he vows to
OL,5,Ckeep them
OL,7,FMr Trump also called on Congress to
OL,8,Fpass a law to prevent any state from
OL,9,Fgranting commercial driving licences
OL,10,Fto illegal aliens and the Save America
OL,11,FAct to prevent "unpermitted persons"
OL,12,Ffrom voting.
OL,14,FIn the longest State of the Union
OL,15,Faddress at one hour and 48 minutes `
OL,16,F19 minutes longer than Bill Clinton's
OL,17,Ffinal address ` he described the US as
OL,18,F"bigger, better, richer than ever
OL,19,Fbefore" and said "this is the golden
OL,20,Fage of America".
OL,26,@sD@POUsD@dO]zD@AOU{D@GO]{D@ROU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
