OL,3,CDonald Trump says countries are
OL,4,C'happy' with tariffs as he vows to
OL,5,Ckeep them
OL,7,FThe Winter Olympic gold medal-winning
OL,8,FUS men's ice hockey team and Erika
OL,9,FKirk ` widow of murdered activist
OL,10,FCharlie Kirk, who Mr Trump said had
OL,11,Fbeen "martyred" ` were among the
OL,12,Finvited guests, but the president was
OL,13,Fnot universally well-received.
