OL,3,CDonald Trump says countries are
OL,4,C'happy' with tariffs as he vows to
OL,5,Ckeep them
OL,7,FTexas Democratic representative Al
OL,8,FGreen was escorted from the chamber
OL,9,Fearly in the speech after unfurling a
OL,10,Fsign which read "Black People Aren't
OL,11,FApes!" as Mr Trump entered, apparently
OL,12,Freferencing a video posted by the
OL,13,Fpresident on social media featuring
OL,14,Fformer president Barack Obama and
OL,15,Ffirst lady Michelle Obama depicted as
OL,16,Fapes.
