OL,3,CDonald Trump says countries are
OL,4,C'happy' with tariffs as he vows to
OL,5,Ckeep them
OL,7,FHe was also heckled by Democrats after
OL,8,Fsaying they should be "ashamed of
OL,9,Fyourselves" after they did not stand
OL,10,Fto support his statement that the
OL,11,Fgovernment's duty was "to protect
OL,12,FAmerican citizens, not illegal aliens".
OL,14,FMr Trump repeatedly asked why they did
OL,15,Fnot stand, called them "crazy", and
OL,16,Fsaid "Democrats are destroying our
OL,17,Fcountry" over young people
OL,18,Ftransitioning gender.
